Package ohos.data.resultset

Class AbsResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.resultset.AbsResultSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResultSet
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbsSharedResultSet, CombinedResultSet, TableResultSet

    public abstract class AbsResultSet
extends Object
implements ResultSet
    The abstract class for basic ResultSet.

    This class provides basic implementation for ResultSet, and is supposed to be extended by ResultSet implementation class.

    Since:
    2
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_APPDATAMGR
